INSERT INTO account_stats(account_id, followers_count, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (?, ?, now(), now()) ON CONFLICT (account_id) DO UPDATE SET followers_count = account_stats.followers_count + ?, updated_at = now() RETURNING id;

INSERT INTO account_stats(account_id, following_count, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (?, ?, now(), now()) ON CONFLICT (account_id) DO UPDATE SET following_count = account_stats.following_count + ?, updated_at = now() RETURNING id;
